{"type": "article", "id": 9831, "title": "Lexon 极简台灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-21T07:08:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235514grJljLFK4AhqmYn8.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t这是 Lexon 推出的一款极简台灯，灯杆采用铝合金管，而灯座则选用的是 ABS 橡胶，材质十分轻盈。灯杆可以旋转 120 度，方便使用者调整角度方便自己的使用以及“拗造型”。同时，这款台灯配备有一个 USB 接口，可以给其他小型电器如手机等电子设备充电。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235511eWZRXO9UlY1aAC5f.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.57701711\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235512gtXYS79yp5GCNMoi.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235512gs1t5BHILhQj9MFf.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235512BGEnyijIVFawkDQM.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235513O03dQwCUHSc9uFoJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235513koWVb4ice2N0sjXM.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}